    <item>
      <title>拜登提供 98 亿美元支持公共交通机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/biden-offers-9-8-billion-to-bolster-public-transit-agencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的政府将向公共交通机构提供 98 亿美元的联邦资金，这是他在 11 月寻求连任时强调对美国基础设施投资的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/biden-offers-9-8-billion-to-bolster-public-transit-agencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷正在与国际货币基金组织讨论新计划大纲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/argentina-is-talking-with-imf-about-new-program-outline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府高级官员表示，阿根廷正在与国际货币基金组织讨论一项可能的新计划的大纲，该计划将带来新的现金，以加速其退出资本管制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/argentina-is-talking-with-imf-about-new-program-outline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 13:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特考虑在预算内延长英国石油和天然气暴利税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/jeremy-hunt-may-extend-uk-windfall-tax-on-oil-gas-at-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特正在考虑延长英国对石油和天然气公司利润征收暴利税的提议，作为正在考虑的几个增加收入的选项之一，以帮助为下周的预算中的个人减税提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/jeremy-hunt-may-extend-uk-windfall-tax-on-oil-gas-at-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 13:06:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
