    <item>
      <title>普京警告北约如果向乌克兰派遣军队将面临核战争风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/putin-warns-nato-of-risk-of-nuclear-confrontation-over-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京警告说，如果北约派遣军队援助乌克兰，北约将面临发生核冲突的风险，在俄罗斯军队发动攻势之际，他加大了对基辅美国和欧洲盟友的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/putin-warns-nato-of-risk-of-nuclear-confrontation-over-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:41:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙数十人等待援助遭袭击，死亡人数突破 30,000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-29/urgent-strike-on-palestinians-waiting-for-aid-in-gaza-kills-and-wounds-dozens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙地带拉法（美联社）目击者称，周四，以色列军队向加沙城一大群正在从援助车队上抢夺食物的巴勒斯坦人开枪。据卫生官员称，已有 100 多人死亡，使以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来的死亡人数达到 3 万多人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-29/urgent-strike-on-palestinians-waiting-for-aid-in-gaza-kills-and-wounds-dozens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 08:58:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
